full_text: By the way, Scherzer is most likely making his home debut on Tuesday the 19th, right? Asking for me and 42,000 friends. #LGM

Game 163 was a special and exciting quirk of the game so of course @MLB gets rid of it in place of a bunch of arbitrary stipulations that no one will remember or be bothered to pay attention to. 🙄 https://t.co/yw0Dw4KHVa

Not a whole lot to say about #AmbuLAnce. It is a gonzo action spectacle of the highest order and I was highly entertained. Tip of the cap to whoever gave Michael Bay a bunch of drones for Christmas. https://t.co/KD9JotnVaM

Today's #FantasticBeasts discourse has reminded me that I am, in fact, seeing the movie tomorrow. I plum forgot! Should've probably rewatched the first two as a refresher but now I'm thinking a quick scan of Wikipedia will suffice.
Looks like every Mets-Phils game is going to give me heartburn this year but I'll take two out of three any way I can get it. BRING ON THE HOME OPENER!!! #LGM https://t.co/783j8IVRG7
